---
import { recentSales, salesStats } from '../data/recentSales';
---

<section class="bg-white px-4 py-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" id="recent-sales">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl overflow-hidden rounded-sm border border-sky-950/10 bg-white shadow-[0_24px_60px_rgba(9,34,52,0.12)]">
    <div class="grid gap-8 bg-linear-to-br from-white via-sky-50/70 to-[#efe7da] px-5 py-8 sm:px-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.35fr] lg:items-start lg:px-10">
      <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-28">
        <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-wide text-sky-700">Proven Results</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-black tracking-normal text-sky-950 sm:text-4xl">A clear record of local performance</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-slate-600">
          At Tad Scott Homes, I pride myself on achieving exceptional results for my clients. Over the past year, I have successfully sold most properties within 30 days and for close to 97% of the asking price. Here is a snapshot of my recent sales performance:
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500">
          Recent closings across Topsail Island and nearby coastal communities show the pace, pricing discipline, and consistency clients can expect.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          {salesStats.map((stat) => (
            <div class="rounded-sm border border-sky-950/10 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
              <strong class="block text-2xl font-black text-sky-950">{stat.value}</strong>
              <span class="mt-1 block text-xs font-bold uppercase leading-5 text-slate-500">{stat.label}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-sm border border-sky-950/10 bg-white shadow-lg shadow-sky-950/10">
        <div class="border-b border-sky-950/10 bg-sky-950 px-4 py-4 text-white sm:px-5">
          <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-wide text-sky-200">Recent sales snapshot</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-sky-50/85">Selected closings across Topsail and surrounding coastal markets.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="max-h-[720px] overflow-auto">
          <table class="min-w-[660px] w-full border-collapse text-left text-xs sm:text-sm">
            <thead class="sticky top-0 bg-sky-950 text-white">
              <tr>
                <th class="px-3 py-3 font-black">Address</th>
                <th class="px-3 py-3 font-black">Days</th>
                <th class="px-3 py-3 font-black">List</th>
                <th class="px-3 py-3 font-black">Sold</th>
                <th class="px-3 py-3 font-black">Sold/List</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              {recentSales.map(([address, days, listing, sold, ratio]) => (
                <tr class="border-b border-sky-950/8 odd:bg-white even:bg-sky-50/70">
                  <td class="px-3 py-3 font-bold text-sky-950">{address}</td>
                  <td class="px-3 py-3 text-slate-700">{days}</td>
                  <td class="px-3 py-3 text-slate-700">{listing}</td>
                  <td class="px-3 py-3 font-bold text-slate-900">{sold}</td>
                  <td class="px-3 py-3 text-slate-700">{ratio}</td>
                </tr>
              ))}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
